+# agyeman-lms
+
+Multi-tenant Next.js LMS (App Router, TypeScript) with host-based routing.
+
+Tenants (subdomain-only for now)
+- default: any host not matched (e.g., app.agyemanenterprises.com)
+- tls: tls.agyemanenterprises.com
+- spm: spm.agyemanenterprises.com
+- sva: sva.agyemanenterprises.com
+
+Behavior
+- No apex domains or 301 redirects are configured yet.
+- TLS and SPM share course catalog with SPM showing upsell to TLS.
+- SVA is isolated.
+
+Key files
+- middleware.ts
+- src/tenants/config.ts
+- src/tenants/provider.tsx
+- src/app/layout.tsx
+- src/app/page.tsx
+- src/services/catalog.ts
+
+Local development
+- npm i
+- npm run dev
+
+Testing tenants locally
+- curl -I -H "Host: tls.agyemanenterprises.com" http://localhost:3000
+- curl -I -H "Host: spm.agyemanenterprises.com" http://localhost:3000
+- curl -I -H "Host: sva.agyemanenterprises.com" http://localhost:3000
+
+Verification (subdomains only)
+- curl -I https://tls.agyemanenterprises.com
+- curl -I https://spm.agyemanenterprises.com
+- curl -I https://sva.agyemanenterprises.com
